head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths HIGGINS, KATIE CASSIDY

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths HIGGINS, KATIE CASSIDY

block.p: HIGGINS-Katie Cassidy. On September 26, 1997, of Rye, New York. Beloved daughter of Timothy and Patricia Higgins. Loving sister of Timothy Martin Higgins of Rye. Dear granddaughter of John and Nancy Cassidy of Rye Brook and the late Walter and Aileen Higgins. Adored niece of Mr. and Mrs. Walter Higgins, Mr. Peter Higgins, Mrs. Joan Chilko, Mr. and Mrs. John Cassidy, Mr. and Mrs. Kevin P. Cassidy, Mr. and Mrs. James Cassidy, Mr. and Mrs. Stephen Mara, Mr. and Mrs. Lawrence Foley, Mr. and Mrs. Vincent Holmes, Mr. and Mrs. Michael F.X. Cassidy, and the late Sean M. Cassidy. Beloved cousin of thirty first cousins. Family will receive friends Sunday 7-9, and Monday 2-4 and 79 PM, at the William H. Graham Funeral Home, 1036 Boston Post Road, Rye. Mass of Christian Burial at the Church of the Resurrection, Tuesday, 10 AM. Interment Gate of Heaven Cemetery.
